{"tha-ap425:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap425:0.2":"Sakimsammajjakavagga ","tha-ap425:0.3":"Ekasanadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap425:1.1":"“Himavantassavidure, ","tha-ap425:1.2":"gosito nama pabbato; ","tha-ap425:1.3":"Assamo sukato mayham, ","tha-ap425:1.4":"pannasala sumapita. ","tha-ap425:2.1":"Narado nama namena, ","tha-ap425:2.2":"kassapo iti mam vidu; ","tha-ap425:2.3":"Suddhimaggam gavesanto, ","tha-ap425:2.4":"vasami gosite tada. ","tha-ap425:3.1":"Padumuttaro nama jino, ","tha-ap425:3.2":"sabbadhammana paragu; ","tha-ap425:3.3":"Vivekakamo sambuddho, ","tha-ap425:3.4":"aganchi anilanjasa. ","tha-ap425:4.1":"Vanagge gacchamanassa, ","tha-ap425:4.2":"disva ramsim mahesino; ","tha-ap425:4.3":"Katthamancam pannapetva, ","tha-ap425:4.4":"ajinanca apattharim. ","tha-ap425:5.1":"Asanam pannapetvana, ","tha-ap425:5.2":"sire katvana anjalim; ","tha-ap425:5.3":"Somanassam paveditva, ","tha-ap425:5.4":"idam vacanamabravim. ","tha-ap425:6.1":"‘Sallakatto mahavira, ","tha-ap425:6.2":"aturanam tikicchako; ","tha-ap425:6.3":"Mamam rogaparetassa, ","tha-ap425:6.4":"tikiccham dehi nayaka. ","tha-ap425:7.1":"Kallatthika ye passanti, ","tha-ap425:7.2":"buddhasettha tuvam mune; ","tha-ap425:7.3":"Dhuvatthasiddhim papponti, ","tha-ap425:7.4":"etesam ajaro bhave. ","tha-ap425:8.1":"Na me deyyadhammo atthi, ","tha-ap425:8.2":"pavattaphalabhojiham; ","tha-ap425:8.3":"Idam me asanam atthi, ","tha-ap425:8.4":"nisida katthamancake’. ","tha-ap425:9.1":"Nisidi tattha bhagava, ","tha-ap425:9.2":"asambhitova kesari; ","tha-ap425:9.3":"Muhuttam vitinametva, ","tha-ap425:9.4":"idam vacanamabravi. ","tha-ap425:10.1":"‘Vissattho hohi ma bhayi, ","tha-ap425:10.2":"laddho jotiraso taya; ","tha-ap425:10.3":"Yam tuyham patthitam sabbam, ","tha-ap425:10.4":"paripurissatinagate. ","tha-ap425:11.1":"Na mogham tam katam tuyham, ","tha-ap425:11.2":"punnakkhette anuttare; ","tha-ap425:11.3":"Sakka uddharitum atta, ","tha-ap425:11.4":"yassa cittam panihitam. ","tha-ap425:12.1":"Iminasanadanena, ","tha-ap425:12.2":"cetanapanidhihi ca; ","tha-ap425:12.3":"Kappasatasahassani, ","tha-ap425:12.4":"vinipatam na gacchasi. ","tha-ap425:13.1":"Pannasakkhattum devindo, ","tha-ap425:13.2":"devarajjam karissasi; ","tha-ap425:13.3":"Asitikkhattum raja ca, ","tha-ap425:13.4":"cakkavatti bhavissasi. ","tha-ap425:14.1":"Padesarajjam vipulam, ","tha-ap425:14.2":"gananato asankhiyam; ","tha-ap425:14.3":"Sabbattha sukhito hutva, ","tha-ap425:14.4":"samsare samsarissasi’. ","tha-ap425:15.1":"Idam vatvana sambuddho, ","tha-ap425:15.2":"jalajuttamanamako; ","tha-ap425:15.3":"Nabham abbhuggami viro, ","tha-ap425:15.4":"hamsarajava ambare. ","tha-ap425:16.1":"Hatthiyanam assayanam, ","tha-ap425:16.2":"saratham sandamanikam; ","tha-ap425:16.3":"Labhami sabbamevetam, ","tha-ap425:16.4":"ekasanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap425:17.1":"Kananam pavisitvapi, ","tha-ap425:17.2":"yada icchami asanam; ","tha-ap425:17.3":"Mama sankappamannaya, ","tha-ap425:17.4":"pallanko upatitthati. ","tha-ap425:18.1":"Varimajjhagato santo, ","tha-ap425:18.2":"yada icchami asanam; ","tha-ap425:18.3":"Mama sankappamannaya, ","tha-ap425:18.4":"pallanko upatitthati. ","tha-ap425:19.1":"Yam yam yonupapajjami, ","tha-ap425:19.2":"devattam atha manusam; ","tha-ap425:19.3":"Pallankasatasahassani, ","tha-ap425:19.4":"parivarenti mam sada. ","tha-ap425:20.1":"Duve bhave samsarami, ","tha-ap425:20.2":"devatte atha manuse; ","tha-ap425:20.3":"Duve kule pajayami, ","tha-ap425:20.4":"khattiye atha brahmane. ","tha-ap425:21.1":"Ekasanam daditvana, ","tha-ap425:21.2":"punnakkhette anuttare; ","tha-ap425:21.3":"Dhammapallankamadaya, ","tha-ap425:21.4":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap425:22.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","tha-ap425:22.2":"yam danamadadim tada; ","tha-ap425:22.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap425:22.4":"ekasanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap425:23.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap425:23.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap425:23.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap425:24.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap425:24.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap425:24.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap425:25.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap425:25.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap425:25.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap425:26.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma ekasanadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap425:27.1":"Ekasanadayakattherassapadanam tatiyam. "}